                    <hr>
                    <div>
                        <article>
<div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'comic sans ms';"><span style="color: #20ca5d; font-size: 300%;"><u>Pein's Paladin Guide (Reworked)!</u></span><br /><br /><img style="max-width: 100%;" src="http://s6.postimg.org/qlntrhb8x/Screenshot_2015_07_01_19_12_39.jpg" alt="" /><br /></span></strong></div>
<span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #20ca5d; font-family: 'comic sans ms';">Hello fellow Irunians, and welcome to my paladin guide! This guide will consist of masses amount of info on gears, abilities and crystas that Paladins tend to use in game in order to make their tanking capabilities at its best. Feel free to add onto the list if you feel that there are new gears or crystas that should be added to the guide. For those that help contribute towards the thread will be given credit at the end. Hopefully the guide will be of use to any future paladins in the making ^^)/&nbsp;</span></strong></span><br /><br />
<div><a style="display: none;"></a><span style="cursor: pointer;">Stat Builds for Paladins</span></div>
<div data-tag="spoiler">
<div><br /><span style="color: #0047ff; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold; font-size: 300%;">Builds:</span><br /><strong style="font-size: medium; color: #0047ff;"><br />These are the builds stat-wise most paladins use within the game, it solely depends on your preference for which build you go for. Remember, all of these builds can tank as long as they have VIT as their main stat.&nbsp;</strong><br /><br /><span style="color: #0047ff; font-size: xx-large;"><strong><u>Guardian Spam Builds</u></strong></span><br /><br /><span style="color: #016d88;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;"><u>VIT/INT/DEX - Magic Sword/Special Sword guardian spam user<br /></u>Pros:</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ High MP Pool</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Can tank Magic mobs better compared to VIT/DEX/STR</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Quick Cooldown between buffs<br />+ Self Heal really useful when there's no bishop, can make use of it due to high MP Pool</span><br /></span>
<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #016d88;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">Cons:</span><br /></strong><span style="font-size: medium;">- Not as much damage compared to VIT/DEX/STR</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Relies on HP Pots/Bishop's heal for spamming Guardian</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Not as much gear selection compared to other builds</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- May feel slow at leveling at first.</span></span></div>
<br /><span style="color: #f70000;"><span style="font-size: large;"><u><strong>VIT/DEX/STR - Normal Sword/Special Sword/Bow guardian spam user</strong></u><br /><strong>Pros:</strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Highest guardian damage between the guardian builds</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Variety of gear selection to choose from</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Quick Cooldown between buffs</span><br /><br /></span>
<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #f70000;"><span style="color: #f70000;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">Cons:</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Lower MP Pool compared to builds that have INT</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Can't tank Magic mobs as well compared to builds that have INT</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Relies on HP Pots/Bishop's heal for spamming Guardian</span><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-size: large;"><br /></span></span></span>
<div style="text-align: left;"><u style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: large;">VIT/INT/AGI - Special Throwing Guardian Spam User</span></u><br /><strong style="font-size: large;">Pros:</strong><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ High MP Pool</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ High Evasion</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Can tank against magic mobs compared to any stat builds without INT</span><br /><br />
<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: large;">Cons</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Auto Attack function is not implemented so your skills will very likely be interrupted with normal attacks<br />- Not a wide selection of equipment to pick from in the case of Special Throwings<br />- Not much damage in Oath and Guardian in comparison to the VIT/STR/DEX build</span></div>
</div>
</div>
<br /><span style="color: #b30373;"><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>VIT/INT/STR - Normal Sword/Cane/Throwing guardian spam user</strong></span><br /><strong>Pros:</strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ High MP Pool</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Can tank Magic mobs better compared to VIT/DEX/STR</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Self heal really useful when there's no bishop, can make use of it due to high MP Pool.</span><br /></span>
<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #b30373;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">Cons:</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Not as much damage in Oath and Guardian compared to Special Sword VIT/DEX/STR paladins</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Slow quick cooldown between buffs compared to builds that have DEX</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Relies on HP Pots/Bishop's heal for spamming Guardian</span></span></div>
<span style="color: #0047ff; font-size: xx-large;"><strong><u>Berserk Spam Builds</u></strong></span><br /><br /><span style="color: #016d88;"><span style="color: #016d88;"><span style="font-size: large;"><u style="font-weight: bold;">VIT/INT/CRT - Magic Sword berserk spam user</u><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Pros:</span></span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ High MP Pool</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Can take magic hits better compared to VIT/STR/CRT</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Longer Berserk duration compared to VIT/STR/CRT</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Good for 1v1 soloing bosses</span><br /></span></span>
<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size: large;">Cons:</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium; font-weight: normal;">- Slow quick cooldown between buffs compared to builds that have DEX<br />- Not as much critical damage dealt compared to VIT/STR/CRT<br />- HP Pot/Mp Pot Reliant when spamming Berserk</span></span></div>
<br /><span style="color: #f70000;"><span style="font-size: large;"><u style="font-weight: bold;">VIT/STR/CRT - Normal Sword berserk spam user</u><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Pros:</span></span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">+ Higher critical berserk damage compared to VIT/INT/CRT</span><br /></span><span style="font-size: medium; color: #f70000;">+ Good for 1v1 soloing bosses<br /></span>
<div style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #f70000;"><strong><span style="font-size: large;">Cons:</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Slow quick cooldown between buffs compared to builds that have DEX</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Will take more magic damage from Mobs compared to VIT/INT/CRT</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- Quicker Berserk duration compared to VIT/INT/CRT</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">- HP Pot/MP Pot Reliant when spamming Berserk</span><br /></span></div>
</div>
</div>
<div><a style="display: none;"></a><span style="cursor: pointer;">Gear Sets for Paladins</span></div>
