<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="color: #0047ff;"><strong style="font-size: x-large;">Armors:</strong><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Saltus (Strengthened x 3):</strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> ATK +8%, MaxHP +14%, MaxMP +10%, magic resistance +8%, HP natural recovery +30%, Heal Reward +8%, Item Recovery +7%. (hidden effect: Items delay -1 seconds)</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Leather Coat (Strengthened x 2):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Auto MP Recovery +50%, Absolute&amp;Magic Evasion +6%, MDEF +15%, Burn Time -0.5s, Heal Reward +1500.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Heinrich Mail (Strengthened x 2):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">ATK +14%, MATK +14%, Melee pierce +6%, Magic pierce +6% Magic evasion +8% Heal reward +1000, Damage cut if HP is under 25% or lower.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;">Weapons:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Jade Ricus:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Auto HP recovery +1000 &amp; +50%, MaxHP +20%, Heal reward +10%, Item recovery +10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Sauro Blade L5:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">ATK +5%, Critical damage +19%, Heal reward +8%, STR +10, VIT +10, Item Delay -1.7 sec, Melee +400, Melee pierce +5%.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">Additional Equipment:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Cataract Helm: </strong><span style="font-size: medium;">ATK&amp;MATK +5%, Heal Reward +10%, Magic attack chance by attack, if Lv &gt; 250, Water Magic +10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Huge Cherry Blossom (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Heal reward &amp; Item recovery +10%, HP absorb chance, MaxHP +12%, MaxMP -8%, ASPD -10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Kontramel:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">INT +3, Heal reward +10%, HP recovery using MP by defense, Burn time -0.5 sec.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Miselatis (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Heal reward +1500 + 5%, DEX +10, Auto recovery +15%, Cast time -20%, Delay -1.2 sec if INT &gt; 249.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Rosa de Amor (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">MATK +10%, Autoskills +7%, Item recovery +15%, MDEF +12%, Cast time +10%, Heal reward +15%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Stier (Strengthened x 2):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">VIT +10, MaxHP +20%, Heal reward +10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Zweig Shield (Strengthened x 2):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Rate cut +22%, VIT +15, Evasion -5%, Heal reward up based on VIT.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;">Crystas:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Botaniga:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Heal reward +100, Heal reward up based on VIT.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Grapagos:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">STR +3, VIT +2, Heal reward +7%, adds Critical damage +14% on Weapons.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Rogelio:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">VIT +5, Melee R +4%, MDEF +5%, Hate Rise +10%, Heal Reward +8%, Ailment R +7%.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">Al Crystas:</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">▲Irai:</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;MaxHP +3%, Melee R +10%, Heal Reward +5%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">▲Heal Reward I:</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;Heal Reward +200</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">▲Heal Reward II:</strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> Heal Reward +400</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">Abilities:</span><br /><br /></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #0047ff;"><strong>☆Heal Reward: </strong>(Adds&nbsp;Heal Reward +100, Heal Reward +1% in the First Tier, adds Heal Reward +50 to a maximum of Heal Reward +300, Heal Reward +1%.)</span><br /></span></span><hr style="color: #0077ff; font-size: x-large; text-align: center;" />
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #7e9600;"><strong style="font-size: xx-large;">☆Item Recovery☆</strong><br /><br /></span>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #7e9600;"><u style="font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;">Armors:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Shiroito-Odoshi (Strengthened x 2):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Critical rate +22 with Swords, Item recovery +25%, ATK +6%, VIT +10, AGI +9.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Saltus (Strengthened x 3):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">ATK +8%, MaxHP +14%, MaxMP +10%, magic resistance +8%, HP natural recovery +30%, Heal Reward +8%, Item Recovery +7%. (hidden effect: Items delay -1 seconds)</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">Weapons:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Thunder Blade Indra+ (Sword):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> Item recovery +25%, ASPD +10%, Evasion +10%, Thunder element.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Legacy of Will II (Sword):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">ATK +18%, MaxHP +15%, MaxMP +15%, Accuracy +15%, Evasion +20%, Melee pierce +18%, Item recovery +15%, ATK up by AGI.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Jade Ricus (Sword):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Auto HP recovery +1000 &amp; +50%, MaxHP +20% Heal reward +10%, Item recovery +10%.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;">Additional Equipment:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Day Pack (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Item Delay -0.7s, Item Recovery +15%, If STR &gt; 300 then additional Item Delay -0.5s, Item Recovery +10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Farmer Belt (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Item recovery +12%, Heal recovery +14%, DEF +100, CRT +10, Hate rise -10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Gloot (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Reflect +10% if VIT &gt; 127. Item delay -1.5 sec, MaxHP +18%, Item recovery +20%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Huge Cherry Blossom (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Heal reward &amp; Item recovery +10%, HP absorb chance, MaxHP +12% MaxMP -8% ASPD -10%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Kanzashi (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">MATK +12%, MaxMP +10%, Magic R +8%, Item recovery +20%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Legion Helm (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Melee R +5%, Magic R +5%, Item recovery +12%, Heal Reward +100, MaxMP -5%</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Lollipop:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Item Recovery +10%, Chance of HP recovery by defense.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Monty Beret (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Melee R +8%, Magic R +8%, Skill delay -1.2 sec, Absolute accuracy +9%, ATK up by DEX, Item recovery +25%, ATK +9%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Rosa de Amor (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">MATK +10%, Autoskill +7%, Item recovery +15%, MDEF +12%, Cast time +10%, Heal reward +15%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Travel Sack (Strengthened x 1):&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Item recovery +30%, Item delay -0.5 sec, Burn, Paralysis and KO Time -0.5sec, DEF up by Lv and MDEF down by Lv.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">Special Equipment:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Angel Earring:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">MaxHP +10%, MaxMP +10%, Ailment R +15%, Item recovery +20% if Lv &gt; 299.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">Sakura Branch:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Absolute&amp;Magic Evasion +5%, Melee&amp;Magic R -5%, Item Recovery +50%, Heal Recovery -100%.<br /><br /><strong>Treatment Technique: </strong>Item Recovery increased. Not applied to special items. (Item Recovery +10%)<br /><br /><strong>Treatment Technique II:</strong> Item Recovery increased. Not applied to special items. (Item Recovery +20%)<br /><br /><strong>Treatment Technique III:</strong> Item Recovery increased. Not applied to special items. (Item Recovery +30%)</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-size: x-large; font-weight: bold;">Crystas:</u><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Dark Santa:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Small MaxHP up by Lv, MP up by Lv, Item recovery +5%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Laster:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">MaxHP +17%, Autoskills -3%, Melee R +3%, Item recovery +15%.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Leese:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Item Recovery -20%, Item delay -0.5 sec, Adds Item Recovery +30% on Armors.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Medical I:</strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> Item recovery +10%, Not applied to special items<br />.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Medical II:</strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> Item recovery +15%, Not applied to special items<br />.</span><br /><br /><strong style="font-size: medium;">◇Medical III:&nbsp;</strong><span style="font-size: medium;">Item recovery +20%, Not applied to special items.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><strong><u style="font-size: x-large;">Al Crystas:</u><br /><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">Rufati:</span></strong><span style="font-size: medium;"> DEF +120, Ailment R +10%, Item recovery +5%.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><u style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">Abilities:</u><br /><br /></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #7e9600;"><strong>☆Pharmacy:</strong> (Adds Item Recovery +2% Per Tier up to the maximum of Item Recovery +10%.)<br /><br /><strong>☆Quick Use:&nbsp;</strong>(Item Delay -0.6 seconds, -5% item recovery, Adds 1% item recovery per Tier negating the minus effect)</span></span></div>
